Marine Curry is quite a famous dish.

102
00:06:38,850 --> 00:06:44,310
Every chef uses their own skills and culture to create a curry for their ship.

103
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:46,820
Hey, sounds tasty!

104
00:06:46,820 --> 00:06:50,620
You've been a trainee cook for half a year, but haven't buit any confidence in yourself.

105
00:06:50,620 --> 00:06:53,160
Just go back and apologize to your chef again.

106
00:06:54,430 --> 00:06:56,150
No!

107
00:06:56,150 --> 00:06:59,340
