114
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:22,250
It's a sea where the fish from all the other oceans swim together!

115
00:07:22,250 --> 00:07:26,490
For cooks, it's a sea of treasure they would risk their lives to see just once!

116
00:07:26,490 --> 00:07:30,300
