224
00:15:41,590 --> 00:15:43,110
Got it guys?

225
00:15:44,750 --> 00:15:46,480
Sanji-san...

226
00:15:46,480 --> 00:15:48,870
...was reminding me about the heat.

227
00:16:04,740 --> 00:16:07,300
Whoa, this is high!

228
00:16:07,300 --> 00:16:10,450
