234
00:16:25,990 --> 00:16:27,640
Add some flour.

235
00:16:29,620 --> 00:16:32,290
Stir gently so it doesn't burn.

236
00:16:37,500 --> 00:16:39,070
Add the curry powder.

237
00:16:40,050 --> 00:16:43,140
Then add Garam Masala to enhance its aroma.

238
00:16:48,630 --> 00:16:51,540
Then combine them all.

239
00:16:54,710 --> 00:16:56,420
Pour in the stock.

240
00:16:58,640 --> 00:16:59,390
Tomatoes.

241
00:17:05,330 --> 00:17:06,790
Add the onions.

242
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:13,470
Then the marinated meat.

243
00:17:36,530 --> 00:17:37,860
No!

244
00:17:39,300 --> 00:17:40,820
