247
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:58,040
Sanji-san!

248
00:18:04,270 --> 00:18:06,160
Damn.

249
00:18:07,140 --> 00:18:08,340
This apple's sweet.

250
00:18:10,290 --> 00:18:11,660
Sanji-san!

251
00:18:12,990 --> 00:18:14,470
