261
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:35,210
That idiot.

262
00:18:35,680 --> 00:18:36,930
After him!

263
00:18:37,710 --> 00:18:42,060
GOMU GOMU NO TOMOZUNA!

264
00:18:43,110 --> 00:18:44,160
Yosh!

265
00:18:44,160 --> 00:18:45,370
I got it!

266
00:18:47,660 --> 00:18:49,130
Tajiyo.

267
00:18:49,330 --> 00:18:52,000
